claim.claim-text:
1. A fiber-reinforced composite material, comprising: 
fibers; 
a surface layer; 
a matrix containing, at least in said surface layer, at least 25 wt % SiC and further phases selected from at least one of the group consisting of Si, Si alloys and C, said matrix having a structure containing at least one of open cracks and pores; and 
at least one metal deposited at least in some of said at least one of open cracks and pores.

